
/*!*
 * Size:
 * `.c-btn_size_{xs|sm|md|lg}` â€” Set button size.
 *
 *
 *     @example.padded
 *     .c-btn.c-btn_color_red.c-btn_size_lg Push me
 *     br
 *     .c-btn.c-btn_color_green.c-btn_size_sm Push me
 *     br
 *     .c-btn.c-btn_color_blue.c-btn_size_xs Push me
 *
